Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.filtering

Provides classes and interfaces defining patterns and matchers and some useful implementations used for filtering objects.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Field
    The Field interface identifies a field of a specific object.
    Filter<T>
    The Matcher interface defines a pattern based filters for objects.
    Matcher<T,​P extends Pattern>
    The Matcher interface defines a pattern based filters for objects.
    Pattern
    The Pattern interface defines a pattern for filtering objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GenericPattern
    The GenericPattern class defines a pattern for filtering any type of object applying some constraints on the value of its fields.
    MessagePatternField
    The SpeechActField class supports the initialization of an optional field of a message pattern.
    OptionalField<T extends Field>
    The OptionalField class supports the initialization of an optional field of an object.
    RegexPattern
    The RegexPattern class defines a pattern for filtering objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GenericMatcher
    The GenericMatcher enumeration defines a pattern matcher that filters objects by applying constraints to the value of its fields.
    MessageMatcher
    The MessageMatcher enumeration defines a pattern matcher that filters messages.
    RegexMatcher
    The RegexeMatcher enumeration defines a pattern matcher that filters objects applying a regular expression to their string representation.
